trans-unit.source: Determines whether a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" /> is placed in the overflow <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />.

If there are more overflow items than can be displayed on the form, use the [ToolStrip Items Collection Editor](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/e681f3ab-94ba-4b2b-ac64-1dfad46caa25) to manage this situation.
trans-unit.target: 더 많은 오버플로 항목 폼에 표시할 수 있는 경우 사용 하 여는 [ToolStrip 항목 컬렉션 편집기](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/e681f3ab-94ba-4b2b-ac64-1dfad46caa25) 이러한 상황을 관리할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" /> is permanently shown in the overflow <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />.

Specifies that a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" /> drifts between the main <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> and the overflow <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> as required if space is not available on the main <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />.
trans-unit.target: 주 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" />에 사용 가능한 공간이 없을 경우 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />이 필요에 따라 주 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />과 오버플로 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" /> 사이를 이동하도록 지정합니다.

trans-unit.source: Specifies that a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" /> is never a candidate for the overflow <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />.
If the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" /> cannot fit on the main <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />, it will not be shown.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripItem" />이 주 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip" />에 들어갈 수 없으면 해당 항목은 표시되지 않습니다.
